ssages containing all keywords: \'transport\', \'Error\', \'while\', \'dialing\' in close proximity.\\nCheck Log: Search for the keyword \'unavailable\' (case-insensitive) in log messages.\\nCheck Metric: Query the `pod_processes` metric for pods belonging to the \'adservice\' service and compare the p99 value during the fault window against the normal baseline.",\n    "Fault Type: adservice-getRandomAds-latency, rrt, rrt_max\\nSymptom: High JVM latency, JVM response delay, elevated request latency, JVM slow response.\\nRoot Cause: Component [adservice] experienced [adservice-getRandomAds-latency, rrt, rrt_max] fault.\\nReasoning: Step 1: Check Metadata - Confirm faulty component is [adservice] (From Ground Truth). Step 2: Check Observation - Found keyword [adservice-getRandomAds-latency] in Log (From GT key_observations). Evidence: Log entries \'AdService-getRandomAds-latency-1749618636 execute()\' (2369 occurrences) and \'Rule.execute called for AdService-getRandomAds-latency-1749618636_33:0\' (2369 occurrences) from pod adservice-0. Step 3: Check Observation - Found keyword [deadlineexceeded] in Log (From GT key_observations). Evidence: Log entries \'failed to get ads: rpc error: code = DeadlineExceeded desc = context deadline exceeded\' from frontend pods, with 2359 total occurrences of \'context deadline exceeded\' status in trace data for AdService calls. Step 4: Check Observation - Found keyword [invocationtargetexception] in Log (From GT key_observations). Evidence: Log entries \'Exception in thread \\"Attach Listener\\" java.lang.reflect.InvocationTargetException\' from adservice pods (adservice-0, adservice-1, adservice-2). Step 5: Check Observation - Found keyword [transformlistener] in Log (From GT key_observations). Evidence: Log entries \'org.jboss.byteman.agent.Transformer : inserted trigger for AdService-getRandomAds-latency-1749618636\' and related Byteman agent transformation logs from adservice pods. Step 6: Check Observation - Found keyword [fron